      *******************************************************
      *------------------------------------------------------
     FABVPL78 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  22 W@MST1
     I                                        1   2 W@MSTA
     I                                        3   4 W@MSTB
     I                                        5  13 W@MSTC
     I                                       14  22 W@MSTD
      *------------------------------------------------------
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@MST1 22
     C                     PARM           P@PACK  50
      *
     C           K#L78     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           W@MST1
      *
      *------------------------------------------------------
      *   M  A  I  N  L  I  N  E
      *
     C                     MOVELP@MST1    W@MST1
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     W@PACK  50
